de.fuberlin.wiwiss.jenaext.impl
Class Index<T>

java.lang.Object
  de.fuberlin.wiwiss.jenaext.impl.Index<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Index2
public class Index<T>
extends Object

Indexes objects by identifiers. The main instantiation of this template is an index of identifier-based triples (IdBasedTriple objects) where the identifiers are the node identifiers. This class can be used to create S, P, and O indexes of triples.

Author:
Olaf Hartig
